edu.snu.onyx.runtime.common.plan.stage

Class Stage

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.snu.onyx.common.dag.Vertex
      • edu.snu.onyx.runtime.common.plan.stage.Stage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public final class Stage
extends Vertex
    Represents a stage in Runtime's execution of a job. Each stage contains a part of a whole execution plan. Stage partitioning is determined by {edu.snu.onyx.compiler.backend.onyx.OnyxBackend}.
